Dear @ymodak ,
Thanks for looking into this issue! I experience the same error. Hope this helps.

  • OS: Windows 10
  • Mobile device: No
  • TensorFlow installed from (source or binary): pip install tensorflow-gpu
  • TensorFlow version: tensorflow-gpu==1.11.0
  • Python version: Python 3.6.6
  • Installed using virtualenv? pip? conda?: Within a virtualenv installed using pip. No conda.
  • Bazel version (if compiling from source): not from source
  • GCC/Compiler version (if compiling from source): not from source
  • CUDA/cuDNN version: cuda 10.0.130_411.31 / cuDNN v7.3.1.20
  • GPU model and memory: Quadro M1000M with 2048MiB
